Updates relating to regulatory changes are given to the Board of Directors & KMP. The topics include:
• Corporate Governance;
• Companies Act & SEBI Listing Regulations;
• Business Process Improvements;
• Code of Conduct;
• Director’s Independence criterion;
• Insider Trading Regulations.

